---
title: Crumbed Halloumi Burger with Caramelised Bacon-Onions & Kūmara Fries
description: Serve up a hearty burger with this version made with a golden "patty" of crumbed halloumi! A smear of smokey aioli and sweet caramelised onion turns this veggie dinner into a taste sensation.

